                <note>2.1 “Sur … 1850 2.3] <hi rend="italic">scored blue crayon</hi>; ‘Read’ <hi rend="italic">in margin blue crayon</hi></note>
                <note>3.1 Lacroix … facts 5.1] <hi rend="italic">crossed blue crayon</hi></note>
